sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Integrator as API Cliente
    participant Discovery as TenantDiscoveryController
    participant Keys as ITenantSigningKeyResolver
    participant Master as SaasMasterDb.Tenants

    Integrator->>Discovery: GET /tenants/{tenantId}/.well-known/openid-configuration
    Discovery->>Keys: ResolvePublicKeyJwk(tenantId)
    Keys->>Master: Ler SigningPublicKeyJwk
    Master-->>Keys: Public JWK
    Discovery-->>Integrator: issuer + jwks_uri + RS256

    Integrator->>Discovery: GET /tenants/{tenantId}/.well-known/jwks.json
    Discovery->>Keys: ResolvePublicKeyJwk(tenantId)
    Keys->>Master: Ler SigningPublicKeyJwk
    Master-->>Keys: Public JWK
    Discovery-->>Integrator: JWKS com public_jwk
    Note over Discovery,Integrator: Nenhum segredo ou chave privada é exposta
